evangelion3.0 — you can (not) redo

A-synchronized real-time campaign site, originally built in 2012,
re-engineered for 2026.

Stack
- Node.js 22 LTS (ESM)
- Express 5
- Socket.IO 4 (WebSocket-first)
- EJS templates
- helmet + compression
- Vanilla JS, Canvas2D (no jQuery / no EaselJS)
- Modern CSS (custom properties, color-mix, container queries, dvh, backdrop-filter)

Run
  npm install
  npm start            # http://localhost:3000
  npm run dev          # node --watch hot reload

Configuration
  PORT=3000
  NODE_ENV=development|production
  RELEASE_AT=ISO-8601 (e.g. 2026-12-17T00:00:00+09:00)

Health
  GET /healthz -> { ok: true, uptime }
